Package org.apache.shardingsphere.distsql.parser.autogen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SingleDistSQLStatementVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by SingleDistSQLStatementParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SingleDistSQLStatementBaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of SingleDistSQLStatementVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
